snippet.title: Lockdown Protocol gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
http://www.fractilegames.com/products/lockdown-protocol/

Lockdown Protocol is a score-oriented platformer/shooter game with multiplayer support and built-in level editor. Available now on Windows and Linux.

Trailer music by Yd (http://opengameart.org/content/spacelife-14)
